5. ARTIFICIAL FASCIA CONCEPT

A high-strength reinforcement mesh positioned between the artificial muscle and the hydraulic skeleton.

Primary functions:

• Mechanical load distribution

• Structural stabilization

• Stress reduction

• Shape retention

• Improved movement efficiency

Potential reinforcement materials:

• Aramid Fibers

• UHMWPE Fibers

• Equivalent high-strength synthetic fibers

